children.name:
AssertionError: 记住密码功能未正常工作，既没有预填用户名也没有自动登录
assert False

AssertionError: 错误的密码组合却仍然注册成功
assert not True
 +  where True = <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB9436E850>>()
 +    where <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB9436E850>> = <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB9436E850>.is_registration_successful

AssertionError: 未填写邀请码却仍然注册成功
assert not True
 +  where True = <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB9441CDD0>>()
 +    where <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB9441CDD0>> = <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB9441CDD0>.is_registration_successful

AssertionError: 使用错误的邀请码却仍然注册成功
assert not True
 +  where True = <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB94420E50>>()
 +    where <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB94420E50>> = <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000001FB94420E50>.is_registration_successful
